  m_Name: Valuable
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  defaultText: I... I don't know about valuable! It's certainly no sunken treasure
    but... I'm glad you think that! I've been enjoying this time together, it's just
    a shame it needs to end... we do need those blankets though.
  conditionalTexts: []
